data.description: Spacious two-story home in the Commons at the Adare.  The Chesney plan offers eat in kitchen, beautiful granite countertops, island & stainless-steel appliances and butler pantry connecting the separate dining room. Enjoy separate formal dining room with coffered ceilings and judges panel and Family room with cozy fireplace & ceiling fan, perfect for family gatherings. Retire upstairs in your oversized master suite with walk in closet. Washing clothes is a breeze with the laundry room right across from the master as well as 3 spacious secondary bedrooms. Close proximity to shops, restaurants, parks and I-75, makes this the perfect place to call home.
